column5: I was wondering if anyone was still looking for a partner this coming year, I would like to fish the Bassmania Eastern series and a couple of the wildcards.
You want to do the BOG one? You got a boat,not that it matters.  Pm  to let me know.
I would like to find someone to fish the whole series with.Isent you a pm

This  year I am pretty much commited,western and 115,s, adding another series to fish, I could be looking at a very small dog house for a long period of time.  Got the pm no problem. Maybe next year we can work something out if ya want.
